msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.175:0.2"
msgid "14. Oghavagga "
msgstr "14. Floods "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.175:0.3"
msgid "175. Anusayasutta "
msgstr "175. Tendencies "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn45.175:1.1"
msgid "“Sattime, bhikkhave, anusayā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these seven underlying tendencies. "

msgctxt "sn45.175:1.2"
msgid "Katame satta? "
msgstr "What seven? "

msgctxt "sn45.175:1.3"
msgid "Kāmarāgānusayo, paṭighānusayo, diṭṭhānusayo, vicikicchānusayo, mānānusayo, bhavarāgānusayo, avijjānusayo—"
msgstr "The underlying tendencies of sensual desire, repulsion, views, doubt, conceit, desire to be reborn, and ignorance. "

msgctxt "sn45.175:1.4"
msgid "ime kho, bhikkhave, sattānusayā. "
msgstr "These are the seven underlying tendencies. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.175:1.5"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, sattannaṃ anusayānaṃ abhiññāya pariññāya parikkhayāya pahānāya … pe … ayaṃ ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo bhāvetabbo”ti. "
msgstr "The noble eightfold path should be developed for the direct knowledge, complete understanding, finishing, and giving up of these seven underlying tendencies.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.175:1.6"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

